180
00:15:33,515 --> 00:15:35,851
So sometimes I jot down reminders on it.

181
00:15:35,935 --> 00:15:37,853
But you know…

182
00:15:38,771 --> 00:15:40,606
I was wondering

183
00:15:40,689 --> 00:15:44,109
